description:
This is a 32 minute workout called 'Central Park Virtual Run: Great Treadmill Scenery for Running or Walking in the New York City Park' from the channel Treadily.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a virtual run around the lower loop of New York City's Central Park on a brisk and sunny morning in early spring. Central Park NYC is one of the most popular running and walking destinations in the world, so this is great treadmill scenery for your workout.  Take in the amazing Manhattan skyline, while passing world renowned places like the Metropolitan Museum and Tavern on the Green. Now you're a new yorker!

#virtualrun #treadmillscenery #newyorkcityvirtualrun...
